data.description: Welcome to your charming 2-bedroom, 1-bath bungalow oasis! This recently updated home offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and classic appeal. Step inside to discover a tastefully recently renovated bathroom.  The heart of this home boasts brand-new hardwood floors flowing seamlessly through the inviting dining room, spacious living room, and both bedrooms.  The kitchen is a culinary dream with its slate tile floor and new a, providing a stylish backdrop to your culinary adventures. Equipped with new appliances, this space is not only functional but also a delight for the aspiring chef. Experience year-round comfort with two heating sources and air conditioning throughout the home, ensuring you and your loved ones stay cozy in every season.  Venture outside to discover a spacious backyard and your covered patio for outdoor enjoyment. The large Amish-built shed features electrical service and heating/AC. This versatile space is ideal for a workshop, studio, or additional storage
